Package: obsidian-couch-sync
Version: 0.1.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-requests
Maintainer: Obsidian Couch Sync contributors <maintainers@example.invalid>
Description: Headless Markdown-to-CouchDB sync for Obsidian
 A command-line tool and optional systemd service for syncing local Markdown
 files into CouchDB using an Obsidian LiveSync-style document layout.
